Name: Space Depression
About the game: You must do your best to protect the world! Destroy all enemies. Get the highest score. We start the game in a dangerously circle. Enemies evolve as time progresses. Green and red bonuses appear when you kill enemies. Green bonuses increase your health. Red bonuses allow you to have different weapons. Clear all the enemies to survive and get the highest score.
